{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea139fcfff","title":"对湖南宁乡农民检举周震鳞问题来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"89c81cece9","index":0,"year":1952,"month":4,"day":8,"articleId":"ea139fcfff"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"9bca4d61ea","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。"},{"id":"8098050db8","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"湖南省宁乡县二区竹山乡全体农民1952年3月13日给毛泽东写信，检举周震鳞解放前剥削压道人民，贪污民财，解放后私藏枪支，将押金抵田强迫细户受田，疏散财物，抵抗减租退押，要求将其女儿从北京押回斗争，要他退还押金等。"}],"contents":[{"id":"08678cec37","type":"title","text":"对湖南宁乡农民检举周震鳞问题来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"9bca4d61ea","type":"paragraph","text":"处理。周总理阅后转李维汉同志阅存。此事以不应当依照农民的意见","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"8098050db8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"7ad797c915","type":"paragraph","text":"四月八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"519288ce17","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]周震鳞，湖南宁乡人，1903年与黄兴组织华兴会，曾任同盟会湘支部长，参加辛玄革命和讨袁护法斗争，后任国民政府委员、国民党中央监察委员。1949年随程潜在湖南起义。新中国成立后任政协第一届全国委员会委员、湖南人民军政委员会顾问。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"badeba53d7","type":"paragraph","text":"这些环事是可能的，但周是老同盟会员，一向不附蒋，现是政协委员，应予以保护。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"683ff36715","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"},{"id":"151a79104a","type":"paragraph","text":"四月八日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff"}],"page":{"id":"67cc5efdc0","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ea139fcfff","start":51,"end":52}}}},"__N_SSG":true}